&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Production-Grade Model Tuning:&lt;/strong&gt; Leading the strategy for when, and if, to move beyond simple prompting. You will oversee supervised fine-tuning (SFT) and Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning (LoRA) workflows to adapt models to our specific product domains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance &amp;amp; Cost Engineering:&lt;/strong&gt; Balancing the &quot;Quality-Cost-Latency&quot; triangle. You will find ways to maintain high-quality outputs while optimizing token usage and reducing inference latency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
